angle choke)\n| |[[2016 in Absolute Championship Berkut#ACB 32: The Battle of Lions|ACB 32: The Battle of Lions]]\n| {{dts|2016|March|26|format=mdy}}\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| 2:18\n| [[Moscow]], Russia\n|\n|-\n| {{no2}}Loss\n| align=center| 21\u201313\u20131 (2)\n| [[Clifford Starks]]\n| Decision (unanimous)\n| [[World Series of Fighting 22: Palhares vs. Shields|WSOF 22]]\n| {{dts|2015|August|1|format=mdy}}\n| align=center| 3\n| align=center| 5:00\n| [[Las Vegas, Nevada]], United States\n|<small>[[Light Heavyweight (MMA)|Light Heavyweight]] bout.</small>\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| align=center| 21\u201312\u20131 (2)\n| Baga Agaev\n| Submission (guillotine choke)\n| Abu Dhabi Warriors 2\n| {{dts|2015|March|26|format=mdy}}\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| 1:55\n| [[Abu Dhabi]], United Arab Emirates\n|\n|-\n| {{no2}}Loss\n| align=center| 20\u201312\u20131 (2)\n| Evgeny Erokhin\n| KO (punches)\n| FEFoMP: Russia's MMA Supercup\n| {{dts|2014|December|20|format=mdy}}\n| align=center| 2\n| align=center| 2:59\n| [[Khabarovsk]], Russia\n|<small>Return to [[Heavyweight (MMA)|Heavyweight]].</small>\n|-\n| {{no2}}Loss\n| align=center| 20\u201311\u20131 (2)\n| [[Anthony Johnson (fighter)|Anthony Johnson]]\n| KO (punch)\n| [[World Series of Fighting 8: Gaethje vs. Patishnock|WSOF 8]]\n| {{dts|2014|January|18|format=mdy}}\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| 2:03\n| [[Hollywood, Florida]], United States\n|<small>[[Light Heavyweight (MMA)|Light Heavyweight]] bout.</small>\n|-\n| {{no2}}Loss\n| align=center| 20\u201310\u20131 (2)\n| [[Andrei Arlovski]]\n| Decision (unanimous)\n| [[World Series of Fighting 5: Arlovski vs. Kyle|WSOF 5]]\n| {{dts|2013|September|14|format=mdy}}\n| align=center| 3\n| align=center| 5:00\n| [[Atlantic City, New Jersey]], United States\n| \n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| align=center| 20\u20139\u20131 (2)\n| [[Travis Wiuff]]\n| KO (punch)\n| CFA 11: Kyle vs. Wiuff 2\n| {{dts|2013|May|24|format=mdy}}\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| 0:21\n| [[Coral Gables, Florida]], United States\n| <small>Return to [[Heavyweight (MMA)|Heavyweight]].</small>\n|-\n| {{no2}}Loss\n| align=center| 19\u20139\u20131 (2)\n| [[Gegard Mousasi]]\n| Submission (rear-naked choke)\n| [[Strikeforce: Marquardt vs. Saffiedine]]\n| {{dts|2013|January|12|format=mdy}}\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| 4:09\n| [[Oklahoma City]], Oklahoma, United States\n| \n|-\n| {{nocontest}}NC\n| align=center| 19\u20138\u20131 (2)\n| [[Rafael Cavalcante]]\n| NC (banned substance)\n| [[Strikeforce: Barnett vs. Cormier]]\n| {{dts|2012|May|19|format=mdy}}\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| 0:33\n| [[San Jose, California]], United States\n| {{small|Original submission loss; overturned by CSAC after Cavalcante tested positive for a banned substance.}}\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| align=center| 19\u20138\u20131 (1)\n| [[Marcos Rog\u00e9rio de Lima]]\n| Decision (unanimous)\n| [[Strikeforce: Barnett vs. Kharitonov]]\n| {{dts|2011|September|10|format=mdy}}\n| align=center| 3\n| align=center| 5:00\n| [[Cincinnati]], Ohio, United States\n| \n|-\n| {{no2}}Loss\n| align=center| 18\u20138\u20131 (1)\n| [[Ant\u00f4nio Silva (fighter)|Ant\u00f4nio Silva]]\n| KO (punches)\n| [[Strikeforce: Henderson vs. Babalu II]]\n| {{dts|2010|December|4|format=mdy}}\n| align=center| 2\n| align=center| 2:49\n| [[St. Louis, Missouri]], United States\n| <small>[[Heavyweight (MMA)|Heavyweight]] bout.</small>\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| align=center| 18\u20137\u20131 (1)\n| Steve Oliver\n| TKO (punches)\n| Xtreme MMA Australia 3\n| {{dts|2010|November|5|format=mdy}}\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| N/A\n| [[Sydney]], Australia\n| <small>Won XMMA Light Heavyweight Championship.</small>\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| align=center| 17\u20137\u20131 (1)\n| Abongo Humphrey\n| Submission (rear-naked choke)\n| [[2010 in Strikeforce#Strikeforce Challengers: del Rosario vs. Mahe|Strikeforce Challengers: del Rosario vs. Mahe]]\n| {{dts|2010|July|23|format=mdy}}\n| align=center| 2\n| align=center| 3:28\n| [[Everett, Washington]],